response.original_title: NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017: Day 11
response.overview: Day 11 of NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017 took place on November 01, 2017, at Saitama City Memorial Gymnasium in Saitama, Japan. The main event featured Los Ingobernables de Japon (BUSHI, EVIL, Hiromu Takahashi, SANADA & Tetsuya Naito) vs CHAOS (Kazuchika Okada, Rocky Romero, SHO, Tomohiro Ishii & YOH). The semi-main event also featured Hiroshi Tanahashi, Katsuya Kitamura & Toa Henare vs Juice Robinson, Kota Ibushi & Tomoyuki Oka. Other wrestlers on the show include Ren Narita, Ryusuke Taguchi and Jushin Thunder Liger, and more!
